OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1782260286
OL,3,CPictures of Peter Murrell's purchases
OL,4,Cwith embezzled funds released
OL,6,FPolice have released a series of
OL,7,Fpictures of the items former SNP chief
OL,8,Fexecutive Peter Murrell bought with
OL,9,Fmoney he embezzled from the SNP,
OL,10,Fincluding a #124,000 motorhome and a
OL,11,F#3,500 wine coaster.
OL,13,FMurrell was sentenced to five years
OL,14,Fand three months in prison for
OL,15,Fembezzling a total of #400,310.65 over
OL,16,Fa 12-year period between August 2010
OL,17,Fand October 2022.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
