OL,3,CPictures of Peter Murrell's purchases
OL,4,Cwith embezzled funds released
OL,6,FHe used the funds to make hundreds of
OL,7,Fextravagant purchases, including cars,
OL,8,Fjewellery, luxury homeware and
OL,9,Fdesigner stationery.
OL,11,FITV News takes a look at some of the
OL,12,Fitems authorities say Murrell bought
OL,13,Fusing SNP funds:
OL,15,FMotorhome (#124,550)
OL,17,FRobotic Mower (#3070)
OL,19,FWine coaster (#3500)
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
